{"tid":394251,"cid":18,"subCid":0,"title":"終於明白點解恭喜蓮子魂歸西天係涼薄","createTime":"2017-09-09T18:48:33.000Z","updateTime":"2017-09-09T18:48:33.000Z","uid":54481,"like":3,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"ffcc456247798b733a1f4e52cf442c06cb3edbfb","tid":394251,"uid":54481,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-09T18:48:33.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">基督徒：自殺既人係要落地獄嫁</span><img src=\"/assets/faces/big/devil.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: blue;\">所以你如果恭喜魂歸西天，就係串緊佢<br />\n恭喜落地獄先係正確既陳述，任何人都唔應該扭曲事實</span></span><br />\n<br />\n所以劉曉波果句係完全冇問題既，因為自然病死，可以魂歸西天<br />\n校方個句「極度遺憾」如無意外應該係講緊共黨唔應該軟禁劉霞<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://scontent.fsin2-1.fna.fbcdn.net/v/t1.0-9/21432911_1606833892715988_2209855986758275007_n.jpg?oh=92042ace4e1f0dbf8b9d66192b0bd7a7&amp;oe=5A19C4D2\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fscontent.fsin2-1.fna.fbcdn.net%2Fv%2Ft1.0-9%2F21432911_1606833892715988_2209855986758275007_n.jpg%3Foh%3D92042ace4e1f0dbf8b9d66192b0bd7a7%26oe%3D5A19C4D2&h=c9e8921e&s={SIZE}\" />"}]}